*Uzeo* je novac iz sefice. (He took the money from the safe.)

*Uzela* je knjigu sa polica. (She took the book from the shelf.)

*Uzimao* je novac iz sefice svaki dan. (He was taking the money from the safe every day.)

*Uzeli* su njegovu torbu. (They took his bag.)

*Uzimam* novac iz sefice svaki dan. (I am taking the money from the safe every day.)